e moving thing.\n```\n\nIn this stanza, the lines \"and becomes less\" and \"until there is nothing left\" are indented.\n\nTherefore, the stanza number with indented lines is **Stanza 3**.\n\n**Answer: The stanza number with indented lines is Stanza 3.**\n\nDoes everyone agree with this analysis, or is there any further clarification needed?"
